Sentencas: Oxygen transport in an LSM/YSZ/LaAlO solid oxide fuel cell type reactor was studied.

Sentencas: The oxygen permeation fluxes under methane feed in the anode side are 1-2 orders of magnitude higher than those under helium feed.
